data.description: This document describes the architecture designed to fulfil the requirements outlined in [CAB RD]. The description of the architecture comprises the definition of functional components and the interfaces/reference points used or exposed by these functional components.

The scope of this document is limited to the Enabler Release Definition of the Converged Address Book (CAB) Enabler according to OMA Release process and the Enabler Release specification baseline listed in section 5.
This document defines the requirements for the Converged Address Book (CAB) Enabler.
